---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 2025';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Stage Companion. We collect zero data.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-text mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-dim text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>

      <div class="prose">
        <!-- Summary -->
        <div class="p-6 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-text mt-0 mb-3">
            The Short Version
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-0">
            <strong class="text-text">We collect zero data.</strong> Stage Companion works completely offline. Your setlists, settings, and usage are stored only on your device. We have no analytics, no tracking, and no accounts. Your data is yours alone.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>None.</strong> Stage Companion does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information or usage data. The app operates entirely on your device without any connection to external servers.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          All data created within the app — including setlists, program configurations, and preferences — is stored locally on your device using Apple's secure storage mechanisms. This data is:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Stored only on your device</li>
          <li>Included in your iCloud backups if enabled</li>
          <li>Deleted when you uninstall the app</li>
          <li>Never transmitted to us or any third party</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Network Access</h2>
        <p>
          Stage Companion does not require or use an internet connection. The only network-related functionality is MIDI communication with your Nord Stage 4 keyboard via USB or Bluetooth, which is a direct local connection.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We do not use any third-party services, analytics platforms, or advertising networks. The app contains no:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Analytics or tracking code</li>
          <li>Advertising SDKs</li>
          <li>Third-party login services</li>
          <li>Crash reporting services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Bluetooth and USB Access</h2>
        <p>
          The app requires access to Bluetooth and USB to communicate with your Nord Stage 4 keyboard. This access is used exclusively for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detecting and connecting to MIDI devices</li>
          <li>Sending MIDI messages (program changes, control changes, clock)</li>
          <li>Receiving MIDI messages (for MIDI Learn functionality)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          No data from these connections is stored, logged, or transmitted.
        </p>

        <h2>Sharing Features</h2>
        <p>
          When you use the setlist sharing feature (QR code or JSON export), the data is shared directly between devices. We do not see, store, or process any shared data.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Since we collect no data, Stage Companion is compliant with children's privacy regulations including COPPA. The app does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under 13.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          If we ever change our data practices, we will update this policy and notify users through the App Store update notes. Given our commitment to privacy, any changes would only be to further strengthen your privacy protections.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:kongsjorden@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">kongsjorden@gmail.com</a>
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Since we don't collect any data, there's nothing to access, correct, or delete. Your data exists only on your device and is fully under your control.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .font-display {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }

  .prose {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    list-style-type: disc;
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .prose a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
